Hartwell, Herbert. THE THEOLOGY OF KARL BARTH: AN INTRODUCTION. Philadelphia, PN: The Westminster Press, 1964.


Polman, A.D.R. Barth. Translated by Calvin D Freeman. Phillipsburg, NJ: Presbyterian and Reformed Publishing Company, 1982.
K˙巴特。《當代歐陸宗教思想系列教會教義學（精選本）》。戈爾維策精選。何亞將、朱雁冰譯。香港：三聯書店有限公司，1996。
